                                                                                                                                                       Symonds future not secure: CA
    Melbourne: Cricket Australia (CA) says Andrew Symonds will have to prove that he is a reformed man, besides performing well on the field, to harbour hopes of a good future. Symonds played in Australia rsquo;s ODI series against Pakistan and was named in the squad for the Twenty20 World Championship In June but CA chief executive James Sutherland said the Queenslander will be on the watch due to his past off-field indiscretions.
